{
  "texts": [
    "This involved the removal of duplicates followed by a detailed manual evaluation of each article to confirm adherence to our predefined inclusion criteria, ensuring a comprehensive and focused review.",
    "We examined the application scenarios, model architecture, data sources, methodologies used, and main outcomes from selected studies on LLMs in mental health.",
    "Firstly, we categorized each study to clarify their primary goals and applications, providing an overview of how LLMs are being utilized in the mental health field.",
    "This categorization helps in understanding the diverse ways in which these models are applied.",
    "Following that the main model architecture of LLMs used was summarized."
  ]
}